                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8935" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0283</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1233 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">向阳而生，逐光而行—隆基绿能的ESG践行之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Born under the sun and following the light - The ESG Practice Path of LONGI</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李纯青，任梦圆，刘伟（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隆基绿能科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；环境；社会；公司治理；利益相关者</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG, Environmental, Society, Governance, Stakeholders</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">基于我国的ESG战略部署、证监会与交易所的ESG信披政策、各方利益相关者对龙头企业社会责任的关注，践行ESG已经成为企业发展过程中的重要一环。作为光伏行业的龙头企业，隆基绿能在其天然的行业优势背景下，尽全力满足各方需求，探索出了一条成熟的ESG践行之路。本案例一方面纵向梳理隆基绿能的ESG践行历程；另一方面，横向梳理隆基绿能最新的ESG开展工作，展现隆基绿能的ESG践行特色，探索其ESG实践所带来的积极效果与示范效应。本案例旨在使学生充分了解ESG的内涵、动因、过程及效果，并通过分析隆基绿能ESG践行之路取得的积极效果，帮助培养学生的责任意识，使其在未来能够结合企业内外部环境变化提升批判性思辨能力，为更多企业的ESG转型之路出谋献策。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Based on China&#39;s ESG strategic deployment, the ESG communication policies of the China Securities Regulatory Commission and the exchange, and the attention of various stakeholders to the social responsibility of leading enterprises, practicing ESG has become an important part of the development process of enterprises. As a leading enterprise in the photovoltaic industry, LONGI has made every effort to meet the needs of all parties and explored a mature path of ESG practice under its natural industry advantages. On the one hand, this case vertically reviews the ESG practice process of LONGI; On the other hand, horizontally reviewing the latest ESG implementation work of LONGI, showcasing its ESG practice characteristics, and exploring the positive effects and demonstration effects brought by its ESG practice. The purpose of this case study is to enable students to fully understand the connotation, motivations, processes, and effects of ESG, and to help cultivate students&#39; sense of responsibility by analyzing the positive effects of LONGI &#39;s ESG practice. This will enable them to improve their critical thinking ability in the future by combining changes in the internal and external environment of the enterprise, and provide suggestions for the ESG transformation path of more enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业ESG实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
